                        <interp inst="t18381231-name-544" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH ALDEE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a sergeant in the Edmonton police. I produce a certificate of the prisoner Banks's former conviction—I was a witness—he is the person who was tried and convicted—(<hi rend="italic">read.</hi>)</p>
